01:53.635 --> 01:56.855
BAYWATCH

02:04.385 --> 02:06.387
"TEQUILA BAY"

02:52.389 --> 02:53.956
DOWN TO THE NEXT ORDER
OF BUSINESS,

02:54.086 --> 02:56.306
OUR POLICY ON STRING BIKINIS.

02:56.437 --> 02:57.873
ALL THOSE IN FAVOR SAY, "AYE!"

02:58.003 --> 02:59.396
AYE!

02:59.527 --> 03:01.224
THE DEFINITION OF BUTTOCKS
IS AS FOLLOWS.

03:01.355 --> 03:04.358
"THE PROTUBERANCE
AT THE REAR OF THE HUMAN BODY

03:04.488 --> 03:07.056
FROM THE UPPERMOST CLEAVAGE
OF THE NATES."

03:07.187 --> 03:08.144
WHAT ARE NATES?

03:08.275 --> 03:11.234
-THESE ARE NATES.
-WHOA!

03:11.365 --> 03:14.368
TO THE LOWERMOST CURVATURE
OF SAID PROTUBERANCE.

03:14.890 --> 03:16.674
-ARE WE ALL CLEAR ON THAT?
-NO!

03:16.805 --> 03:20.417
IF YOU SEE ANY PORTION OF SKIN
FITTING THAT DESCRIPTION,

03:20.548 --> 03:21.810
CONTACT MITCH IMMEDIATELY!

03:21.940 --> 03:24.291
NO, IT'S A $50 FINE.

03:24.421 --> 03:25.596
OH!

03:25.727 --> 03:27.685
AND NOW
FOR MY LAST ANNOUNCEMENT.

03:28.686 --> 03:30.993
I WOULD LIKE TO ANNOUNCE
THAT THIS WILL BE

03:31.123 --> 03:33.343
MY LAST ANNOUNCEMENT
AT OUR MORNING BRIEFINGS.

03:33.474 --> 03:35.084
WHAT?

03:35.215 --> 03:36.694
FROM NOW ON, IF YOU HAVE
ANY PROBLEMS WITH SCHEDULING,

03:37.304 --> 03:39.523
HEALTH INSURANCE,
YOUR LOVE LIFE--

03:39.654 --> 03:40.872
BORING AS IT MAY BE--

03:41.003 --> 03:44.180
CONTACT THE NEW
SUPERVISING LIEUTENANT.

03:44.311 --> 03:46.138
THE COUNTY FINALLY SPRUNG?

03:46.269 --> 03:47.792
WHAT BEACH WAS HE FROM?

03:47.923 --> 03:49.490
YOUR GUESS IS AS GOOD AS MINE.

03:49.620 --> 03:51.187
ALL I KNOW
IS THE SECOND HE SHOWS UP,

03:51.318 --> 03:54.408
MY FEET ARE BACK IN THE SAND
PERMANENTLY, WHERE THEY BELONG.

03:55.757 --> 03:57.454
OKAY, EVERYBODY, THAT'S IT.
HAVE A GREAT DAY.

03:57.585 --> 03:58.803
AND WEAR LOTS OF SUN BLOCK.

03:58.934 --> 04:00.414
IT'S GOING TO BE
OVER 100 OUT THERE.

04:01.415 --> 04:05.245
SUMMER, YOU ARE GOING TO OBSERVE
HERE AT HEADQUARTERS WITH BEN.

04:05.375 --> 04:06.811
THIS GUY KNOWS MORE
ABOUT LIFEGUARDING

04:06.942 --> 04:08.596
THAN ANYBODY I KNOW.

04:08.726 --> 04:10.902
SUMMER, I'M GONNA SHOW YOU
HOW TO WRESTLE AN OCTOPUS.

04:11.033 --> 04:13.862
-HAVE A GOOD ONE.
-YEAH, YOU TOO.

04:13.992 --> 04:16.255
MATT, HOW'D YOU LIKE
TO GO SURFING TODAY?

04:16.386 --> 04:17.692
YOU'RE KIDDING ME?

04:17.822 --> 04:19.259
YOU CAN SURF, CAN'T YOU?

04:19.694 --> 04:21.435
IT'S ONE OF THE THINGS
I DO THE BEST.

04:21.870 --> 04:23.175
YOU EVER SURF TEQUILA BAY?

04:23.785 --> 04:25.526
TOO MANY WORMS IN THAT BOTTLE.

04:25.656 --> 04:27.267
YEAH, LOCAL WORMS WHO THINK
THEY OWN THE BEACH.

04:27.397 --> 04:28.920
PUT A COUPLE OF SURFERS
FROM THE VALLEY

04:29.051 --> 04:30.182
IN THE HOSPITAL YESTERDAY.

04:30.313 --> 04:31.967
NOBODY'S TALKING
TO ANY OF THE LIFEGUARDS.

04:32.097 --> 04:33.403
WE THOUGHT MAYBE YOU COULD GET
A COUPLE NAMES.

04:33.969 --> 04:34.839
YEAH, WHY NOT?

04:35.449 --> 04:36.624
NAME THAT WORM.

04:37.102 --> 04:38.930
JUST DON'T LET THEM PLAY
PINOCHLE ON YOUR SNOUT.

04:39.583 --> 04:40.715
WE LEAVE IN FIVE MINUTES.

04:45.241 --> 04:46.938
WHEN IS IT MY TURN TO DRIVE?

04:48.157 --> 04:50.420
IF AND WHEN YOU MAKE IT
OUT OF ROOKIE SCHOOL.

04:50.551 --> 04:53.205
COME ON. I'VE BEEN RACING
MUSCLE BOATS SINCE I WAS 12.

04:53.336 --> 04:55.120
WELL, THAT WAS A LONG TIME AGO,
WASN'T IT?

04:55.251 --> 04:57.122
HOW OLD ARE YOU? 17?

04:57.253 --> 04:58.602
HOW OLD ARE YOU?

04:58.733 --> 05:01.605
OLD ENOUGH TO SEPARATE
THE MEN FROM THE BOYS.

05:02.432 --> 05:03.390
OH.

05:03.955 --> 05:05.087
THERE'S TEQUILA BAY.

05:05.914 --> 05:07.872
JUST GONNA PULL AROUND THE POINT
AND DROP YOU OFF.

05:08.003 --> 05:09.570
OKAY.

05:15.053 --> 05:18.709
NOW, REMEMBER, YOU'RE NOT
A LIFEGUARD YET, SO NO HEROICS.

05:18.840 --> 05:20.494
THE FIRST SIGN OF TROUBLE,
JUST ACTIVATE THIS TRANSMITTER

05:20.624 --> 05:21.582
AND I'LL COME GET YOU.

05:22.147 --> 05:23.584
[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

05:23.714 --> 05:24.585
WHAT?

05:25.325 --> 05:26.717
I SAID,
"I CAN'T WAIT FOR TROUBLE."

05:51.786 --> 05:53.265
WHO'S THAT GUY?

06:09.499 --> 06:10.587
WHERE'D YOU COME FROM?

06:11.414 --> 06:13.677
HAWAII. PADDLED THE WRONG WAY.

06:13.808 --> 06:14.765
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

06:15.679 --> 06:17.333
I USUALLY SURF
WHEN NO ONE'S OUT.

06:18.290 --> 06:19.291
SO, ARE YOU ONE OF THE SHOOTERS?

06:19.422 --> 06:20.510
NEVER HEARD OF 'EM.

06:20.641 --> 06:22.599
THEY CLAIM THEY OWN THESE WAVES.

06:23.252 --> 06:24.732
WAVES BELONG
TO WHOEVER'S ON THEM.

07:02.770 --> 07:06.687
THIS PLUG GOES THERE.

07:08.253 --> 07:11.953
AND THIS ONE GOES THERE.

07:15.870 --> 07:17.045
OH, NO.

07:17.175 --> 07:18.220
SUMMER, CAN YOU GET
MITCH ON THE PHONE?

07:18.350 --> 07:19.917
HE'S IN THE GARAGE.

07:20.048 --> 07:21.702
WILL YOU ASK HIM TO COME UP HERE
RIGHT AWAY, PLEASE?

07:24.444 --> 07:27.403
NOW I SEE WHY THEY CALL THIS
AN OCTOPUS.

07:32.539 --> 07:33.453
STEPHANIE?

07:35.367 --> 07:37.935
BEN! BEN, HOW ARE YOU?

07:38.501 --> 07:41.156
FINE.
HANGING ON LIKE A BARNACLE.

07:41.286 --> 07:45.029
BUT YOU--JUST LOOK AT YOU.

07:45.160 --> 07:46.814
AT ME OR AT MY UNIFORM?

07:48.163 --> 07:49.686
HEY, BEN! SUMMER SAID...

07:52.297 --> 07:53.560
HELLO, MITCH.

07:57.172 --> 07:59.261
NOT MUCH HAS CHANGED AROUND HERE
IN THREE YEARS.

08:00.175 --> 08:01.437
CERTAINLY NOT YOU.

08:01.568 --> 08:03.395
STILL FLUFFED AND BUFFED.

08:08.183 --> 08:10.315
I REALIZE HOW AWKWARD THIS IS.

08:10.446 --> 08:12.143
IF I'D KNOWN I WAS GOING TO BE
TRANSFERRED TO BAYWATCH,

08:12.274 --> 08:14.058
I NEVER WOULD HAVE ACCEPTED
THIS ASSIGNMENT.

08:14.189 --> 08:16.234
IT'S NOT TOO LATE
TO CHANGE YOUR MIND.

08:17.235 --> 08:18.541
YOU'RE GOOD AT THAT.

08:19.499 --> 08:21.109
I WORKED HARD
FOR THIS PROMOTION.

08:23.764 --> 08:24.808
DO WHAT YOU WANT.

08:26.070 --> 08:27.463
I'M SURE YOU WILL ANYWAY.

08:30.727 --> 08:31.989
MITCH.

08:32.120 --> 08:33.294
MITCH!

08:36.472 --> 08:38.953
IT TOOK HIM A LONG TIME
TO GET OVER YOU.

08:43.217 --> 08:45.307
CAUTION EMERGENCY VEHICLE

09:01.149 --> 09:01.976
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

09:05.153 --> 09:07.198
FEEL LIKE BOGART
IN "CASABLANCA."

09:08.983 --> 09:10.506
OF ALL THE BEACHES
IN ALL THE TOWNS

09:10.637 --> 09:13.030
IN ALL THE WORLD,
SHE HAS TO WALK INTO MINE.

09:15.598 --> 09:16.773
THANKS.

09:57.901 --> 09:58.728
AHEM.

10:01.426 --> 10:02.558
AM I ON THE WRONG SIDE
OR ARE YOU?

10:02.689 --> 10:05.474
UH,
THIS IS THE MEN'S LOCKER ROOM.

10:05.605 --> 10:07.171
THE WOMEN'S LOCKER ROOM
IS ON THE OTHER SIDE.

10:07.302 --> 10:09.260
OH, SORRY.

10:15.658 --> 10:17.051
I'M STEPHANIE HOLDEN.

10:17.181 --> 10:18.748
I'M SUBBING FOR JILL
WHILE SHE'S ON VACATION.

10:18.879 --> 10:20.358
OH, UM--

10:21.142 --> 10:22.926
I'M MITCH BUCHANNON.

10:23.057 --> 10:24.362
WELCOME TO BAYWATCH.

10:24.972 --> 10:26.451
THANK YOU.

