28:01.375 --> 28:02.811
BODY GLOVE

28:45.419 --> 28:47.638
HEY, THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG
WITH THAT GUY!

28:47.769 --> 28:49.597
HE'S IN TROUBLE!

29:21.150 --> 29:22.630
HE WENT DOWN AROUND HERE.

29:47.742 --> 29:49.657
MITCH, HE'S HAVING SOME
SORT OF A SEIZURE.

29:50.963 --> 29:52.878
-HOLD HIM UP.
-I GOT HIM.

29:54.183 --> 29:55.489
LET'S GET HIM IN.

30:01.800 --> 30:04.237
MAKE SURE HE SEES HIS OWN DOCTOR
BEFORE YOU RELEASE HIM.

30:05.281 --> 30:06.152
THANKS.

30:07.936 --> 30:10.156
I NEED A BLANK MAJOR
INCIDENT REPORT, PLEASE.

30:13.463 --> 30:14.813
OR WOULD YOU RATHER
I FILL IT OUT?

30:15.596 --> 30:16.466
I'LL DO IT.

30:18.425 --> 30:20.035
WE WORKED TOGETHER
PRETTY WELL OUT THERE.

30:21.820 --> 30:23.473
YOU'RE A GOOD LIFEGUARD.

30:23.604 --> 30:24.823
CARE TO PUT THAT IN WRITING?

30:26.955 --> 30:28.261
CHIEF THORPE JUST INFORMED ME

30:28.391 --> 30:29.784
THAT IN ORDER
TO REMAIN AT BAYWATCH

30:29.915 --> 30:31.699
YOU HAVE TO GIVE ME
A LETTER OF ENDORSEMENT.

30:32.482 --> 30:34.093
THIS TIME I GUESS
YOU GET TO DECIDE

30:34.223 --> 30:35.703
IF I STAY OR IF I LEAVE.

30:37.096 --> 30:40.534
LETTER OF ENDORSEMENT REQUIRES
YOU TO STATE SPECIFIC REASONS.

30:43.015 --> 30:45.060
BEFORE I GIVE MINE,
I WANT TO KNOW YOURS.

30:47.149 --> 30:49.064
WHY DIDN'T YOU COME TO CATALINA?

30:50.109 --> 30:51.153
WHY'D YOU LEAVE?

30:53.025 --> 30:54.330
BECAUSE I WAS MARRIED.

30:56.767 --> 30:57.986
WE'D BEEN SEPARATED
FOR TWO MONTHS

30:58.117 --> 30:59.596
WHEN I MET YOU.

30:59.727 --> 31:01.947
AND THE NIGHT BEFORE CATALINA,
HE CAME TO SEE ME

31:02.077 --> 31:04.340
AND PLEADED WITH ME
TO TAKE HIM BACK,

31:04.471 --> 31:06.342
TO GIVE OUR MARRIAGE
ANOTHER TRY.

31:07.996 --> 31:09.171
I'D SEEN THE PAIN
THAT YOU'D GONE THROUGH

31:09.302 --> 31:10.651
WITH YOUR DIVORCE

31:10.781 --> 31:13.610
AND I FIGURED THAT
IT WAS WORTH SAVING.

31:15.351 --> 31:17.223
TURNS OUT THAT I WAS WRONG.

31:18.485 --> 31:20.226
WE GOT DIVORCED A YEAR AGO.

31:21.531 --> 31:23.011
YOU SHOULD HAVE TOLD ME.

31:23.794 --> 31:25.057
I KNOW.

31:25.187 --> 31:27.189
I KNOW,
I JUST COULDN'T FACE YOU.

31:28.451 --> 31:29.888
AND THEN I WANTED TO CALL AND...

31:32.455 --> 31:34.327
THE LONGER I WAITED,
THE HARDER IT GOT.

31:35.502 --> 31:36.938
AND THEN IT WAS JUST TOO LATE.

31:41.160 --> 31:42.901
I GOTTA GET BACK TO MY TOWER.

31:43.466 --> 31:44.772
WAIT. MITCH. MITCH.

31:46.252 --> 31:47.644
IF YOU CAN'T GIVE ME
THAT LETTER OF ENDORSEMENT,

31:47.775 --> 31:48.732
I'LL UNDERSTAND.

31:52.040 --> 31:54.477
BUT I HOPE THAT SOMEDAY
YOU'LL BE ABLE TO FORGIVE ME.

32:06.402 --> 32:07.447
I SHOULD NEVER EVEN
HAVE TOLD YOU GUYS

32:07.577 --> 32:08.709
THAT GUY CAME BACK HERE.

32:08.839 --> 32:10.754
YEAH, WELL, YOU DID,
SO SHUT UP ABOUT IT.

32:10.885 --> 32:12.756
BUT BARBED WIRE?

32:12.887 --> 32:14.323
THAT COULD SLICE HIM UP
PRETTY BAD.

32:14.454 --> 32:16.151
THAT'S THE WHOLE POINT.

32:17.065 --> 32:18.501
THIS IS OUR BEACH.

32:18.632 --> 32:20.547
OUR WATER!

32:20.677 --> 32:21.417
IF WE DON'T DEFEND IT,
WE'RE GOING TO HAVE JELLYFISH

32:21.548 --> 32:22.984
LIKE HIM ALL OVER THE PLACE!

32:23.115 --> 32:25.030
THAT GUY COMES BACK AGAIN,

32:25.160 --> 32:26.857
HE'S GONNA BE CHUM
FOR THE SHARKS.

33:06.506 --> 33:07.986
BODY GLOVE

33:11.728 --> 33:13.339
CATALINA ISLAND FERRY

33:59.037 --> 34:00.690
PAPERWORK AT THIS HOUR?

34:01.735 --> 34:02.649
WELL, YOU'RE UP EARLY.

34:04.564 --> 34:05.826
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU
BEACH PEOPLE?

34:05.956 --> 34:07.306
WHY DO YOU INSIST ON WAKING UP

34:07.436 --> 34:08.697
AT THIS UNGODLY HOUR?

34:08.829 --> 34:10.744
SO YOU PAVEMENT PEOPLE
DON'T BOTHER US.

34:10.873 --> 34:11.831
YEAH, WELL, YOU BOTHER US.

34:11.962 --> 34:13.225
BESIDES, IT'S WAY TOO EARLY

34:13.355 --> 34:14.487
TO TAKE DOWN
FOUR TEQUILA SHOOTERS.

34:14.617 --> 34:15.922
I THOUGHT YOU DIDN'T HAVE
ENOUGH EVIDENCE

34:16.054 --> 34:17.706
TO BUST THOSE SURF PUNKS.

34:17.838 --> 34:19.143
I DON'T, BUT I FIGURED
YOU COULD HELP ME GET SOME.

34:19.274 --> 34:21.059
IF YOU'RE NOT TOO BUSY
PUSHING YOUR PEN.

34:21.623 --> 34:22.842
THIS CAN WAIT.

34:22.973 --> 34:23.974
LET'S DO IT.

34:41.688 --> 34:44.255
[CHATTERING]

34:48.303 --> 34:50.391
LOOK, JUST CONCENTRATE
ON EVERYTHING I TOLD YOU,

34:50.523 --> 34:52.655
AND JUST TRY TO BECOME
PART OF THE WAVE.

34:52.786 --> 34:54.047
YOU'LL BE FINE.

34:58.574 --> 35:00.185
DON'T WORRY ABOUT THEM.
THEY'RE AFTER ME.

35:05.146 --> 35:06.278
MAN, WHAT'S THE DEAL WITH YOU?

35:06.408 --> 35:07.496
ARE YOU LIKE A HEAD CASE

35:07.627 --> 35:09.194
OR ARE YOU JUST REAL STUPID?

35:09.324 --> 35:11.761
LOOK, I'M A LOS ANGELES COUNTY
LIFEGUARD.

35:11.892 --> 35:13.415
WE DON'T WANT ANY TROUBLE HERE,
OKAY?

35:13.546 --> 35:15.287
YEAH, WELL, THEN WHY YOU COME
LOOKING FOR IT?

35:15.417 --> 35:17.941
WE DIDN'T. WE CAME TO SURF
AND THIS IS A PUBLIC BEACH.

35:18.072 --> 35:19.595
THIS IS OUR BEACH!

35:19.726 --> 35:22.250
YOU WANT A PIECE OF ME?
LET'S TAKE IT OUT THERE.

35:22.859 --> 35:24.209
JUST THE TWO OF US.

35:24.339 --> 35:27.560
LOSER DISAPPEARS,
NEVER SHOWS HIS FACE HERE AGAIN.

35:28.387 --> 35:29.910
SUMMER, TAKE MY VAN
AND GET OUT OF HERE.

35:30.040 --> 35:31.520
NO, I'M GONNA STAY AS A WITNESS.

35:31.651 --> 35:33.653
THEN WATCH WHAT HAPPENS
TO YOUR BOYFRIEND.

35:34.958 --> 35:36.699
-LET'S GO.
-LET'S GO, BUDDY.

35:40.573 --> 35:41.704
OFF THE POINT.

36:12.605 --> 36:14.172
OFF THE POINT.

36:52.166 --> 36:53.036
OH!

36:57.171 --> 36:58.346
GET A SCARAB OUT HERE.

36:59.042 --> 37:01.523
KMF295, WE NEED THE SCARAB
AT TEQUILA BAY.

37:26.896 --> 37:27.854
HELP!

37:27.984 --> 37:29.159
HERE, GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

37:29.986 --> 37:31.249
DON'T COME TOO CLOSE.

37:31.379 --> 37:32.380
IT'S SHARP.
IT'S WRAPPED BEHIND ME.

37:32.511 --> 37:33.338
GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

37:37.690 --> 37:38.995
HE'S CAUGHT ON BARBED WIRE.

37:39.126 --> 37:40.258
GRAB THE CAN.

37:43.435 --> 37:45.175
-READY?
-READY.

37:55.577 --> 37:57.013
RUN ME BY HIM!

38:04.891 --> 38:06.980
-I CAN'T GET LOOSE.
-IT'S OKAY.

38:07.546 --> 38:09.069
WE'LL GET YOU OUT. JUST HANG ON.

38:09.199 --> 38:10.766
-I GOT THE WIRE CUTTERS.
-DO IT!

38:24.563 --> 38:25.868
-I THINK MATT'S GOT HIM.
-OKAY.

38:29.176 --> 38:30.438
GET A CHOPPER OUT HERE!

38:30.569 --> 38:31.831
THERE'S ONE ON THE WAY!

38:55.637 --> 38:57.247
HERE'S A PRESENT FOR YOU.

38:57.378 --> 38:59.467
I'LL SEE YOU AROUND, LIFEGUARD.

39:06.256 --> 39:08.650
WHAT I SAID ABOUT
BECOMING PART OF THE WAVE,

39:08.781 --> 39:10.391
THIS ISN'T WHAT I MEANT.

39:11.827 --> 39:13.742
IT'S OKAY, MAN. COME ON.

39:47.863 --> 39:49.996
DIDN'T I TELL YOU
TO STAY AWAY FROM MY DESK?

39:53.565 --> 39:55.480
I SUPPOSE THE REAL QUESTION
IS HOW FAR AWAY?

39:56.045 --> 39:58.221
OVER THERE?
OR ON SOME OTHER PLANET?

40:03.662 --> 40:05.664
IS THAT GOING TO BE A LETTER
OF ENDORSEMENT OR REJECTION?

40:05.794 --> 40:07.230
DO YOU MIND?

40:25.161 --> 40:26.206
RUN OUT OF VENOM?

40:38.740 --> 40:40.307
I THINK IT'S ONLY FAIR
THAT YOU READ THIS

40:40.438 --> 40:42.527
BEFORE I SEND IT
TO CHIEF THORPE.

40:47.445 --> 40:49.098
I DON'T WANT TO GET
TO CLOSE TO YOUR DESK.

40:49.229 --> 40:50.709
GO ON. READ IT.

40:55.453 --> 40:57.106
"WITH REGARDS TO LIEUTENANT
STEPHANIE HOLDEN'S

40:57.237 --> 40:59.674
PERMANENT ASSIGNMENT
TO BAYWATCH HEADQUARTERS,

41:00.414 --> 41:02.764
I FIND IT IMPOSSIBLE NOT TO"--

41:03.678 --> 41:05.245
"I FIND IT IMPOSSIBLE
NOT TO ENDORSE

41:05.375 --> 41:07.160
LIEUTENANT HOLDEN
WHOLE-HEARTEDLY.

41:08.770 --> 41:10.380
SHE'S ONE OF THE MOST
TALENTED AND DEDICATED

41:10.511 --> 41:12.165
LIFEGUARDS
I'VE EVER WORKED WITH,

41:12.295 --> 41:14.515
AND WILL BE A VALUABLE ADDITION
TO THIS HEADQUARTERS."

41:16.343 --> 41:17.649
OH, MITCH.

41:18.737 --> 41:20.042
WELCOME TO BAYWATCH.

41:21.914 --> 41:22.958
THANK YOU.

41:27.789 --> 41:31.314
